{
  "@context": {
    "kairos": "https://darpa.mil/i2o/kairos.official.namespace/",
    "schemas": "kairos:schemas",
    "super": "kairos:super",
    "name": "kairos:name",
    "comment": "kairos:comment",
    "description": "kairos:description",
    "version": "kairos:version",
    "sdf_version": "kairos:sdf_version",
    "privateData": "kairos:privateData",
    "steps": "kairos:steps",
    "subevent": "kairos:subevent",
    "slots": "kairos:slots",
    "role": "kairos:role",
    "constraints": "kairos:constraint",
    "aka": "kairos:aka",
    "location": "kairos:location",
    "order": "kairos:order",
    "before": "kairos:before",
    "after": "kairos:after",
    "container": "kairos:container",
    "contained": "kairos:contained",
    "overlaps": "kairos:overlaps",
    "flags": "kairos:flags",
    "ros": "https://rosario.com/kairos/"
  },
  "schemas": [
    {
      "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario",
      "comment": [
        "Scenario E:",
        "1. Taxi driver trying to stop a drug deal",
        "2. Taxi driver killed",
        "3. Riots start against foreigners in South Africa",
        "4. Looting and destruction of foreigners’ properties and businesses",
        "5. Hundreds arrested and at least 10 deaths",
        "6. Mosque attacked",
        "7. At the end 680 people were arrested",
        "",
        "ros:FullRiotScenario in which (A) precedes (B) precedes (C) (there may be more than one sub-event in each A, B.C)",
        " - (A) Cause event (could be anything) --> This is a type of sub-event, or maybe the first step. Here we have 1,2",
        " - (B) Social unrest event(s) --> There could be several of these. Do they count as 2nd step but you may have several 2nd steps??",
        "       Here we have 3, 4 (subevent of 3?), 5, 6",
        " - (C) Conclusion event / Legal or Social implications (last step). Event 7."
      ],
      "super": "kairos:Schema",
      "name": "Full Riot Scenario",
      "description": "Incident(s) lead to social unrest, with legal/social implication(s)",
      "version": "4/27/2020",
      "sdf_version": "0.5",
      "steps": [
        {
          "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/cause_events",
          "@type": "kairos:Events/SuperEvent",
          "comment": [
            "The event(s) which caused a riot",
            "Do we need a way to specify 1+ events?"
          ],
          "subevents": [
            {
              "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/cause_event1",
              "@type": "ros:Events/PreventActionAttempt",
              "comment": [
                "\"1. Taxi driver trying to stop a drug deal\"",
                "Something akin to https://tac.nist.gov/tracks/SM-KBP/2019/ontologies/EventsWithFringe#Prevent_Action",
                "Could rework this to be a kairos:Events/Impede event."
              ],
              "provenance": "Performer-specific info that tracks the origin of the event.",
              "slots": [
                {
                  "name": "preventer",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/cause_event1/preventer",
                  "role": "ros:Events/PreventActionAttempt/Roles/Preventer",
                  "constraints": [
                    "kairos:PER",
                    "kairos:ORG",
                    "kairos:GPE"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "prevented",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/cause_event1/prevented",
                  "role": "ros:Events/PreventActionAttempt/Roles/Prevented",
                  "constraints": [
                    "kairos:PER",
                    "kairos:ORG",
                    "kairos:GPE"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "topic",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/cause_event1/topic",
                  "role": "ros:Events/PreventActionAttempt/Roles/Topic",
                  "constraints": [
                    "kairos:Event"
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/cause_event2",
              "@type": "kairos:Events/Life/Die",
              "aka": "kill",
              "reference": "https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q844482",
              "comment": [
                "\"2. Taxi driver killed\"",
                "Could be a Conflict.Attack subclass instead"
              ],
              "slots": [
                {
                  "name": "victim",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/cause_event2/victim",
                  "role": "kairos:Events/Life/Die/Roles/Victim",
                  "constraints": [
                    "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/cause_event1/preventer"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "place",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/cause_event2/place",
                  "role": "kairos:Events/Life/Die/Roles/Place",
                  "constraints": {
                    "location": "https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q258"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/social_unrest_events",
          "@type": "kairos:Events/SuperEvent",
          "comment": [
            "\"Social unrest event(s) --> There could be several of these.\"",
            "Do we need a way to specify 1+ events?"
          ],
          "subevents": [
            {
              "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event1",
              "@type": "ros:Events/Riot",
              "comment": [
                "\"3. Riots start against foreigners in South Africa\"",
                "ros:Events/Riot subclasses kairos:Conflict.Demonstrate.  Could also inherit from Conflict.Attack."
              ],
              "slots": [
                {
                  "name": "rioter",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/unrest_event1/rioter",
                  "role": "ros:Events/Riot/Roles/Rioter",
                  "super": "kairos:Conflict.Demonstrate/Roles/Demonstrator",
                  "constraints": [
                    "kairos:PER"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "target",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/unrest_event1/target",
                  "role": "ros:Events/Riot/Roles/Target",
                  "constraints": {
                    "@type": [
                      "kairos:PER",
                      "kairos:FAC"
                    ],
                    "location": "https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q258"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "name": "place",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/unrest_event1/place",
                  "role": "ros:Events/Riot/Roles/Place",
                  "super": "kairos:Conflict.Demonstrate/Roles/Place",
                  "constraints": {
                    "@type": [
                      "kairos:FAC",
                      "kairos:LOC"
                    ],
                    "location": "https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q258"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "name": "cause",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/unrest_event1/cause",
                  "role": "ros:Events/Riot/Roles/Cause",
                  "super": "kairos:Conflict.Demonstrate/Roles/Topic",
                  "constraints": [
                    "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/cause_events"
                  ],
                  "comment": "Ideally we'd like to constrain to the superevent as above, but might need to specify its subevents."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event2",
              "@type": "ros:Events/Looting",
              "comment": [
                "\"4. Looting and destruction of foreigners’ properties and businesses\"",
                "Perhaps ros:Events/Looting subclasses kairos:ArtifactExistence.Destroy and/or Conflict.Demonstrate"
              ],
              "reference": "https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q192623",
              "slots": [
                {
                  "name": "looter",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/unrest_event2/looter",
                  "role": "ros:Events/Looting/Roles/Looter",
                  "constraints": [
                    "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/unrest_event1/rioter"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "target",
                  "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Slots/cause_event2/target",
                  "role": "ros:Events/Looting/Roles/Target",
                  "constraints": [
                    "kairos:FAC"
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event3",
              "@type": "ros:Events/Arrest",
              "comment": [
                "\"5. Hundreds arrested and at least 10 deaths\"",
                "The rest of this subevent is omitted for brevity."
              ]
            },
            {
              "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event4",
              "@type": "kairos:Conflict.Attack",
              "comment": [
                "\"6. Mosque attacked\"",
                "Not sure if this means the building or the people inside it...likely both.",
                "The rest of this subevent is omitted for brevity."
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "@id": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/conclusion_event",
          "@type": "ros:Events/Arrest",
          "comment": [
            "\"7. At the end 680 people were arrested\"",
            "Should this be in a subevent block because there could be more than 1?",
            "The rest of this subevent is omitted for brevity."
          ]
        }
      ],
      "order": [
        {
          "comment": "\"1 precedes 2\"",
          "before": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/cause_event1",
          "after": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/cause_event2"
        },
        {
          "comment": [
            "\"(1,2) precedes/causes 3\"",
            "notice that the 'before' is the superevent containing cause_events 1 and 2"
          ],
          "before": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/cause_events",
          "after": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event1",
          "flags": "causal"
        },
        {
          "comment": "\"3 has SUB-SCHEMA 4\"",
          "container": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event1",
          "contained": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event2",
          "flags": "subevent"
        },
        {
          "comment": "\"(3,4) precedes (5, 6)\"",
          "before": [
            "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event1",
            "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event2"
          ],
          "after": [
            "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event3",
            "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event4"
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "\"7 follows (2, 5, 6)\"",
          "before": [
            "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/cause_event2",
            "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event3",
            "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/unrest_event4"
          ],
          "after": "ros:FullRiotScenario/Steps/conclusion_event"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}